#X text 9 318 V/Oct Math: 1 Volt = 1 Octave. We add the knob and the input jack together \, multiply by 12 to get semitones \, and add 60 to anchor 0V to Middle C. Finally \, [mtof~] converts that MIDI note into an exact frequency for the oscillator, f 27;
