#X text 213 6 Polyphony is automatic. You only need to build a single monophonic voice in Pd. The wrapper automatically clones the patch up to 16 times in C++. A polyphonic cable in VCV Rack instantly drives multiple independent voices. Enable polyphony via the build.py prompt.;
#X text 679 315 The _adc2 suffix tells the layout script to draw the adc~ 2 input jack directly below the Drive knob., f 37;
#X text 431 223 The attenv_ prefix creates a bipolar Attenuverter (-1 to +1). This lets the user scale the CV input up \, turn it down \, or turn it left to completely invert the incoming envelope, f 50;
#X text 279 635 Unassigned dac~ 1 \, without a dummy [s name_dacN @hv_param] \, will automatically create the output jack in the bottom right corner.;
